## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of comprehensive data on women's roles, as historical narratives have often marginalized their contributions. Additionally, the focus on prominent events and organizations may overlook the grassroots efforts and individual contributions of many women who played crucial roles in the struggle against apartheid. Further research could provide a more nuanced understanding of these contributions.